description: This is a negrisk market group over which team will win the Dota 2: PGL Wallachia 2024 tournament.

markets.description:
The PGL Wallachia tournament for Dota 2 is scheduled to take place over October 4-13, 2024. Find more info about the tournament here: https://blast.tv/dota/tournaments/pgl-wallachia-season-2

This market will resolve to "Yes" if Tundra Esports wins this tournament. Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".

If this team is eliminated from the competition based on the official rules of the tournament, this market will resolve to “No”.

If the winner of the PGL Wallachia tournament is not determined by October 27, 2024, 11:59 PM ET, this market will resolve to "No".

The primary resolution source for this market is information provided directly from Blast.tv and official footage of the tournament; however, other credible reporting may be used.
